## Summary
This documentation details the integration between Amplitude and TheTradeDesk, allowing advertisers to send user cohorts for targeted advertising campaigns with support for various ID mapping options (GUID, device ID, or UID2) and a 30-day TTL for synced users that refreshes with each sync.

